ZH: 老化是一個自然過程。
EN: Aging is a natural process.

ZH: 她的皮膚在老化，變得越來越皺。
EN: Her skin is aging and becoming more wrinkled.

ZH: 隨著老化，我們的身體功能逐漸下降。
EN: As we age, our bodily functions decline gradually.

ZH: 環境因素可以影響細胞老化的速度。
EN: Environmental factors can affect the rate of cellular aging.

ZH: 營養豐富的食物可以緩解老化的速度。
EN: Nutrient-rich foods can slow down the aging process.

ZH: 老化主要是由於細胞功能的退化。
EN: Aging is mainly caused by the deterioration of cellular function.

ZH: 運動可以幫助緩解肌肉老化的問題。
EN: Exercise can help alleviate muscle aging problems.

ZH: 健康生活方式可以延緩整體老化的速度。
EN: A healthy lifestyle can delay the overall aging process.

ZH: 防曬是預防皮膚老化的重要措施。
EN: Sunscreen is an important measure to prevent skin aging.

ZH: 老化會影響我們的記憶力和認知能力。
EN: Aging can affect our memory and cognitive abilities.

ZH: 老化可能導致骨骼更脆弱。
EN: Aging may lead to more brittle bones.

ZH: 老化使得皮膚失去彈性。
EN: Aging causes the skin to lose elasticity.

ZH: 老化也會引起肌肉萎縮。
EN: Aging can also cause muscle atrophy.

ZH: 某些食物可以幫助預防細胞老化。
EN: Certain foods can help prevent cellular aging.

ZH: 潔淨的環境可以降低老化對皮膚的影響。
EN: A clean environment can reduce the impact of aging on the skin.

ZH: 老化會降低我們的新陳代謝速率。
EN: Aging can decrease our metabolic rate.

ZH: 研究表明，避免壓力可以延緩老化的速度。
EN: Studies have shown that avoiding stress can slow down the aging process.

ZH: 定期運動可以幫助美容防止老化。
EN: Regular exercise can help to prevent aging and maintain beauty.

ZH: 老化可能使得我們的身心健康下降。
EN: Aging can lead to a decline in our physical and mental health.

ZH: 某些保養品可以幫助減緩皮膚老化的速度。
EN: Certain skincare products can help slow down the rate of skin aging.
